title: The Complete Collection Of MTV’s Headbangers Ball: Watch 1,215 Videos from
excerpt: Premiering in April 1987, MTV's Headbangers Ball featured music videos from metal and hard rock bands of the 80s and 90s--everyone from AC/DC and Mötley Crüe, to Ozzy Osbourne, Def Leppard and Twisted Sister, to Judas Priest, Iron Maiden and Van Halen.
